{"tid":1792572,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解現代音樂界裡面，作曲家既地位冇歌手咁高?","createTime":"2019-12-21T17:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T09:05:54.000Z","uid":128761,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"224ab3a7d28a79132dfda24d1c13b7aadfd77f9d","tid":1792572,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"當你諗起一首現代曲既時候，總會諗起係邊個唱<br />\n但好多時都唔會知道邊個作曲...<br />\n有時都幾鄧佢地唔抵<br />\n冇作曲家，歌手連唱既機會都冇<br />\n但冇歌手，作曲家既作品依然可以有好多既方式表達出黎<br />\n<br />\n明明以前既年代，你只會係識邊首鋼琴曲、小提琴曲係邊個作<br />\n又或者係演奏家 - 作曲家既XXXX，例如Yundi li - Chopin Nocturne Op. 9 No. 2<br />\n而作曲家既地位，又係超過演奏家<br />\n<br />\n黎到現代，唔係應該都係咁架咩？<br />\n版權、收益，應該係作曲家最多，之後作詞，最後先係歌手"},{"pid":"b4d5c1534dda71887cbc9e091f955e361122aea3","tid":1792572,"uid":35637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:56:14.000Z","msg":"pop song姐<br />\n唔睇流行曲 edm又好 indie都好 詞其實已經唔係最重要"},{"pid":"f393af9f1f91c16c14299e2a3ac77a3ba817afa8","tid":1792572,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:56:56.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解1223稅局冇人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7grryiG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7grryiG.jpg&h=5fde20aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj